title: Compilation problems for arm32 and armhf

content.raw:
There are currently some problems with builds on ARM in latest branches of Gazebo \(starting from gazebo9\):

For **arm64**: there is a [linking problem ](https://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo9-debbuilder/488/consoleFull#-17116017516ea37b8d-a6d4-40ae-8431-d90c018842af)for static lib
